// with the fix word, so findFuzzyNeighbor() never considers them). They
// FAIL pre-sync (zero findings — missing expected) and PASS post-sync after
// the sibling-repo rule-library expansion lands the new firstPairTranspose
// pattern. The recall delta is exactly these 6 cases going from red → green.
